response.original_title: Watcha Clan - Live at Cabaret Rouge
response.overview: Watcha Clan is a french group mixing ragga dub electro and jungle influences.  They released on May 23, 2001 a LIVE CD with an extra track video of one of their emblematic song, "Larshuma".
